<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Hai bang ka ngak Zion vangkhuo,
 Lal lenna thangvan gam nuom;
 Suihlung len in ka gal thil a ,
 Nuoi simlei nungtieng sawn in.

[V2]
 Aw, gam thiengtho hinna gam vak,
 Lalna gam ninnuom ka ngai ie,
 Thuong ka tun ma hin Lal nunnem
 Na chawnban in ei kai zingin.

[V3]
 2. Chung sang a lengin tha a zak,
 Natna leh lungkhamna ten;
 Thihna tang sipa chuong I hiu,
 Hinna gam galdawt hitiu.

[V4]
 3. Damlai khawvel hi thil tiem u.
 Lungngaih meipi thim bang zing
 Lei gam pela hin thak ngai in,
 Ka kap Lal nunnem ma ah,

[V5]
 4. Len pul khuom bang do hi Lalpa,
 Ei nem in, suihlung damna'n;
 Pham ngaih lenkawl a thieng zo tai,
 Zion gam chu thil hitiu.</lyrics>
<title>Zion Vangkhuo</title>
<hymn_number>228</hymn_number>
</song>